<div type="translation" resp="part:emfr">
	
	<p n="1">Prosperity!</p>
	
	<p n="1">...</p>	
	<p n="1">This is the manner in which
	...
	have given, after making a donation document.</p>	
	<p n="1-4">We have given
		...</p>	
	<p n="4">In this manner ...</p>	
	<p n="4"><supplied reason="lost">These</supplied> are the signature <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>eḻuttu</foreign><note>Literally, the letters.</note> </supplied>of I, ...</p>	
	<p n="4">The glorious Gopīnātha, this <supplied reason="subaudible">is his</supplied> signature <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>oppam</foreign></supplied>.</p>	
	<p n="4">He who protects this pious donation <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>taṉmam</foreign></supplied>, <supplied reason="subaudible">his</supplied> glorious two feet are on my head.</p>	
	
</div>
	
